<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html charset=us-ascii"></head><body style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; "><div>Hi Folks,</div><div><br></div><div>We are hosting the 4th Community-wide Upgrade Day on the 25th and 26th of September, 2013 (across multiple timezones) to help those of you running older versions of the platform get upgraded to the most stable version of Ushahidi (v2.7.1).</div><div><br></div><div><b>Why should you Upgrade?</b></div><div><p class="MsoNormal">This release featured the following fixes:-</p><ul><li><span style="text-indent: -18pt; ">Bulk deletions coupled with single report deletion</span></li><li><span style="text-indent: -18pt; ">Login page issues Date picker issues in default theme</span></li><li><span style="text-indent: -18pt; ">Database table prefix installation issues</span></li><li><span style="text-indent: -18pt; ">Some Custom form issues Image upload issues (uploading jpegs, image sizing issues)</span></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal">Here is the&nbsp;<a href="http://blog.ushahidi.com/2013/09/04/ushahidi-version-2-7-1-bamako-bug-fix-release/">blog post announcement on the v2.7.1 release</a>, as well complete list of the fixes tagged under the&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/ushahidi/Ushahidi_Web/issues?milestone=11&amp;page=1&amp;state=closed">2.7.1 milestone on our github issues page.</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>Get help, or be a helper!</b></p><div><a href="https://docs.google.com/a/ushahidi.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AisCbUDEZly6dGxFN0JvNm8ya2NxTHpKQmVycklocWc#gid=0">Sign up on the upgrade day schedule</a>&nbsp;if you need help upgrading, or can help someone in need. Be sure to add in your contact information.</div><div><br></div><div>For reference purposes, here are some resources on the&nbsp;<a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Upgrading+Ushahidi">upgrade process&nbsp;</a>and&nbsp;<a href="https://wiki.ushahidi.com/display/WIKI/Migrating+to+a+newer+Ushahidi+version">migrating to a newer version of Ushahidi</a>.</div></div><div><br></div><div>If you upgrade your deployment or help the community upgrade, please add this to your social media or blogs.</div><div><br></div><div><img height="500" width="500" apple-width="yes" apple-height="yes" id="3fa511ac-da68-41ac-a634-aaaf05dc40bb" src="cid:FE9EE02E-F745-492E-AA42-2D7D093A2663"></div><div><br></div><div>Hope you can join us on Skype and IRC!</div><div><br></div><div>Fabulous week ahead, folks!</div><div apple-content-edited="true"><div style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; "><div style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; "><div style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; "><div style="word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; "><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 11px; ">Angela Oduor.</span></font><div><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 11px; "><span style="border-collapse: separate; "><span style="border-collapse: collapse; "><font><font><a href="http://www.ushahidi.com/" target="_blank">Ushahidi Inc</a>.</font><font><br>Platforms:&nbsp;<a href="http://ushahidi.com/" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 65, 112); ">Ushahidi</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://crowdmap.com/" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 65, 112); ">Crowdmap</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;</font></font></span></span><span style="border-collapse: separate; "><span style="border-collapse: collapse; "><font><a href="http://ushahidi.com/products/swiftriver-platform" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 65, 112); ">SwiftRiver</a></font></span></span><span style="border-collapse: separate; "><span style="border-collapse: collapse; "><font>&nbsp;<a style="color: rgb(17, 65, 112); background-repeat: repeat repeat; "><img style="width: 12px; border-width: medium; border